There is no internet in the room, but if you have an laptop with WIFI you can go downstair in the hotel lobby / waiting area, you will receive free internet there.	Another excellent feature was free internet available in the lobby (you could pay for internet in your room, but I can't see why you would do this).	The internet service, which I ordered from my room, was dodgy and I didn't have time for a technician to come up to sort it out, so I never did get it.	Wireless internet is available in the lobby, although quite a few times I had trouble connecting to it.